I always assumed my respect for you is clear.

639
01:03:20,276 --> 01:03:22,471
我们之间这么多年的谈话历历在目...
Dialogue we have had across the years...

640
01:03:22,472 --> 01:03:26,285
别说了，史波克
It's okay, Spock.You don't have to say it.

641
